<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi,</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">An occured with eTouches interface while creating a Campaign Member.&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Log is registered with id&nbsp;<b>{!Interface_Log__c.Name}</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Created by:&nbsp;{!Interface_Log__c.CreatedBy}</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Date log:&nbsp;{!Interface_Log__c.Date_Log__c}</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Related service :<b>&nbsp;{!Interface_Log__c.Interface_Name__c}</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Detailed error message (response):</div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!Interface_Log__c.Error__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Message/Data concerned:</div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!Interface_Log__c.Data__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">eTouches process Id (if relevant):</div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!Interface_Log__c.Process_Id__c}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">These information can be retrieved in Salesforce with the following url:</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>{!Interface_Log__c.Link}</b></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Regards</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><br></div>]]></td>
